item.dc:creator: @hidendra Hidendra
item.description:
@hidendra wrote:

If you want to find random spots, then find someplace, even if its water, no clip, and run. Whenever you get loading - please wait screen, no clip again. Don’t just run for a few seconds.
You’ll be amazed at some things you can find that aren’t just at the teleports mentioned above.
